BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:s2Np84iUJxjUinwpFVKnD
SUMMARY:TADAIMA: I'm Home
DTSTAMP:20260325T193728Z
DTSTART:20260330T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:After more than 80 years\, a treasured collection returns “home
	” to Seattle’s Japanese American community. In 1942 dozens of traditional 
	Boys’ and Girls’ Day dolls were entrusted to Bailey Gatzert Elementary Sch
	ool by Japanese American families facing forced incarceration. Most were n
	ever reclaimed after the war. Artist Miya Sukune uses recent research in M
	OHAI’s collection\, as well as interviews with Japanese American survivors
	 and their descendants\, to create an installation called “Tadaima\,” mean
	ing “I’m home.”\n\nTADAIMA: “I’m Home!” Bringing Seattle’s Girls’ and Boys
	’ Day Dolls Home reconnects the dolls with their traditional role of prote
	cting and blessing children. It invites visitors to celebrate the resilien
	ce\, memory\, and enduring traditions of the Japanese American Community.\
	n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/tadaima-i-m-home/18096356
	/2026-03-30T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/tadaima-i-m-home/18096356
	/2026-03-30T00
LOCATION:Museum of History and Industry\, 860 Terry Ave N\, Seattle\, Seatt
	le\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-arts
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT7H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Ehmdd0m47dzS1azDYwxlK
SUMMARY:Family Story Time
DTSTAMP:20260325T193728Z
DTSTART:20260330T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Monday\, March 30\, 2026\, 10:30 - 11am\n\nAt storytime\, kids 
	ages 0-5 and their families can enjoy stories\, songs\, and fun learning a
	ctivities.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nGreen Lake Branch\n\nRegistration Required
	: Registration is not required.\n\nDetailed Description: Early Learning is
	 a great way for kids ages 0-5 and their families to develop learning\, li
	teracy\, and language skills as well as community with other families.\, W
	e read stories\, sing songs\, and have engaging\, educational activities t
	hat help kids and their caregivers grow together.\n\nEvent Logistics: Ask 
	our staff for your free\, same-day tickets prior to our program.\, Registr
	ation is not required but these programs are very popular and the room cap
	acity can fill up quickly.\, Families of all ages are welcome\, though thi
	s early learning program is intended for youth aged 0-5\, their caregivers
	 and families.\, Find out more about\n\nEarly Learning & Story Time\n\npro
	grams.\,\n\nContact Us: If you have questions about this event\,\n\nAsk Us
	\n\nor call 206-386-4636.\n\nADA Accommodations: We can provide accommodat
	ions for people with disabilities at Library events. Please\n\ncontactLEAP
	\n\nat least seven days before the event to request accommodations.\, All 
	Library programs are free and open to the public.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amc
	ity.com/events/#/details/family-story-time/18228704/2026-03-30T00\n\nFrom 
	SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/family-story-time/1822870
	4/2026-03-30T00
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-arts
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - Arts & Culture
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT30M
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:H9QkNSCx5ZXlcWbngtGJp
SUMMARY:Caleidoscopio Juega y Aprende
DTSTAMP:20260325T193728Z
DTSTART:20260330T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Monday\, March 30\, 2026\, 10 - 11:30am\n\nLos niños escuchan c
	uentos multilingües\, cantan canciones y hacen manualidades sencillas con 
	sus cuidadores durante el tiempo en grupo.\n\nEste programa se realizará ú
	nicamente en\n\nespañol.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nDelridge Branch\n\nRoom Loca
	tion: Sala de reuniones\n\nRegistration Required: No se requiere inscripci
	ón.\n\nDetailed Description: El Caleidoscopio Juega y Aprende ofrece a los
	 niños y sus familias la oportunidad de venir a jugar y pasar un buen rato
	.\, También hay un tiempo de juego para que los niños exploren diversos ju
	guetes y actividades infantiles.\, Los niños aprenden y exploran el uso de
	l arte\, la música\, los juguetes y mucho más. Las familias aprenden sobre
	 el desarrollo de sus hijos y los recursos comunitarios que tienen a sus d
	isposición.\, Agradecemos a nuestro socio\n\nVilla Comunitaria .\,\n\n----
	----------------------------------------\, Kaleidoscope Play & Learn offer
	s a chance for children and their families to come play and have a good ti
	me.\, There is also a play time for children to explore various toys and p
	lay activities.\, Children learn and explore the use of art\, music\, toys
	 and more. Families learn about their child&'s development and community r
	esources available to them.\, Thanks to our partner\n\nVilla Comunitaria .
	\n\nEvent Logistics: Este grupo está dirigido a niños de 0 a 5 años de tod
	as las habilidades.\, Caleidoscopio Juega y Aprende es para familias\, ami
	gos\, vecinos que cuidan niños\, padres y los niños a su cargo.Este progra
	ma no está diseñado para dejar a los niños solos y no es adecuado para gua
	rderías\, centros preescolares u otras organizaciones dedicadas al cuidado
	 de niños.\, Obtenga más información sobre los programas\n\nAprendizaje te
	mprano y la hora de cuentos .\,\n\n---------------------------------------
	-----\, This group is open to children of all abilities\, ages 0 to 5 year
