	their families are invited to join our drop-in play group with Lego bricks
	\, Picasso tiles\, and other building sets.\n\nLocation Link:\n\nNewHolly 
	Branch\n\nRoom Location: Meeting Room\n\nRegistration Required: Registrati
	on is not required.\n\nDetailed Description: We'll bring the building supp
	lies. You bring your imagination! At this drop-in event\, children and the
	ir families are invited to play with the library&'s collection of LEGO\, L
	EGO DUPLO\, and MEGA BLOKS.\n\nEvent Logistics: Families of all ages are w
	elcome\, though this program is intended for youth aged 3-10\, their careg
